@page "/theming"

<NBTitle Variant="@NBTitleVariant.Title">Theming</NBTitle>
<NBTitle Variant="@NBTitleVariant.Subtitle">Customize colors, shadows and typography via CSS variables or NBThemeProvider.</NBTitle>

<NBTitle Variant="@NBTitleVariant.Section">Option A — NBThemeProvider</NBTitle>
<p>Wrap any subtree with <code>NBThemeProvider</code>. Only properties you set will override the defaults. You can nest multiple providers for different sections.</p>

<CodeBlock Code="@CS.ThemingProvider" />

<NBTitle Variant="@NBTitleVariant.Section">Option B — CSS override</NBTitle>
<p>Override the variables directly in your stylesheet:</p>

<CodeBlock Language="css" Code="@CS.ThemingCssOverride" />

<NBTitle Variant="@NBTitleVariant.Section">Token reference</NBTitle>

